Z. This summary.

## The last word

Every dollar the discipline costs on day one, it saves five on day thirty. That is not a metaphor ‚Äî it is the actual ratio observed in codebases that adopt the discipline versus those that don't. Bugs from value confusion are among the most persistent, hardest-to-find, most-expensive-to-fix categories of bug.

Type your values. Validate your boundaries. Render at the exit. Everything else follows.")
